vote.title: An ordinance setting the tax rate at $0.7765 per $100 assessed valuation which includes $0.5690 for the General Fund and $0.2075 for the Debt Service Fund, and levying ad valorem taxes for the City of Dallas, Texas for FY 2020-21 - Estimated Levy: $1,144,898,917 (see Fiscal Information)
